snippet.title: Observo | First Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Observo is an upcoming short indie horror game styled after early 2000s horror game classics. Developed by SpaceZeta Games, it tells the story of a man who finds a roadside inn to spend the night in at the last minute, but finds himself in danger when strange things start happening inside the place.

Coming this year (2022) for PC.

Official website:
https://spacezeta.com.br/observo
Follow for updates:
https://twitter.com/spacezetagames
